              { "key": "X-Killbill-ApiSecret", "value": "{{api_secret}}" },
              { "key": "X-Killbill-CreatedBy", "value": "postman" }
            ],
            "description": "Step 1 of 7: Set clock to reference date.\nThen run the requests above in order:\n  03 → Create account\n  04 → Create subscription\n  00 → Set clock to 2026-02-05 (advance past trial)\n  06 → Get account invoices (confirm setup+base appear)\n  05 → Record usage\n  00 → Set clock to 2027-02-05 (period end)\n  06 → Get single invoice (confirm USAGE item)\n  07 → Get account overdue state\n  08 → can-proceed? check"
          }
